{"tid":1013220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰王室史上第一人！67歲豔麗公主角逐總理大位　震撼泰政壇","createTime":"2019-02-08T07:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T11:48:15.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9f7af85c01939b9acb24d59b9b645dbc47b1b608","tid":1013220,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3885/d3885614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3885%2Fd3885614.jpg&h=d2a1de2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 烏汶叻公主經常在公開場合亮相。（圖／路透）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n泰國總理大選即將在3月24日登場，今（8日）是候選人登記的最後一天。泰愛國黨（Thai Raksa Chart Party）宣布提名泰國公主烏汶叻（Princess Ubolratana Rajakanya）參選總理，為泰國政壇投下震撼彈，因為這是首次有泰國王室成員參選。現任軍政府總理帕拉育（Prayut Chan-o-cha）也在今天接受公民力量黨（PPRP）提名，但外界認為，他將面臨嚴峻挑戰。<br />\n泰愛國黨黨魁布伊查普（Preechapol Pongpanich）表示，烏汶叻公主受過良好教育，且能力極佳，是最適合擔任總理的人選。但依據泰國傳統慣例，王室成員通常不涉入政治，她此次參選打破政壇傳統。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3885/d3885615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3885%2Fd3885615.jpg&h=1e0bdeb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泰愛國黨是為泰黨的分支，由流亡海外的前總理兄妹檔戴克辛（Thaksin Shinawatra）與盈拉（Yinglak Shinawatra）親戚盟友成立的新政黨。（圖／路透）<br />\n烏汶叻公主現年67歲，是已故泰王蒲美蓬（Bhumibol Adulyadej）與王后詩麗吉（Queen Sirikit）的長女，出生於瑞士，小時候有著「法國娃娃」的綽號。但長大後的她多了「學霸公主」的稱號，因為她先後取得美國麻省理工學院（MIT）數學理科學士學位，以及加州大學洛杉磯分校（UCLA）公共衛生學碩士學位。<br />\n烏汶叻公主經常精心打扮在公開場合亮相，但在1972年7月25日放棄王室頭銜，嫁給念書時期認識的美國人詹森（Peter Jensen），她自此之後在美國生活長達26年，2人育有3個孩子，直到1988年婚姻關係結束後，她才回到泰國，且仍被視為王室的一份子。<br />\n▼ 烏汶叻公主經常出席公開活動，積極參與慈善工作。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3885/d3885616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3885%2Fd3885616.jpg&h=9084d952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3885/d3885617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3885%2Fd3885617.jpg&h=5c2ed9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190208/1374157.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190208%2F1374157.htm&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1EoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=f4cf0d51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190208/1374157.htm</a>"},{"pid":"516c2f2407b42cd6c778e5739d7b39a4e9bba24b","tid":1013220,"uid":212399,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:41:55.000Z","msg":"@棋靈王"},{"pid":"b2666922fada25ae4519fb1b8978210bb01c4f8c","tid":1013220,"uid":13678,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:42:32.000Z","msg":"已經改變唔倒泰國女人係有鳩嘅印象"},{"pid":"93a5852bd9f9a4565ba7090c4777ca0950fae5ff","tid":1013220,"uid":206437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗秦王"},{"pid":"19601c12739447cd8518842b7aabc4f17ab98134","tid":1013220,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93a5852bd9f9a4565ba7090c4777ca0950fae5ff","tid":1013220,"uid":206437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗秦王"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"66c6b64b62034d16b2221a592f1735f92dd8fc74","tid":1013220,"uid":2110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"君主立憲制既國家但忽然皇權同政權合一返，覺得一定出事，除非真係為理想，如果唔係依d三煞位做黎把鬼，遲下敗埋泰皇留落既威望"},{"pid":"df125331f0de6ce857593666e0cb57d55b36f551","tid":1013220,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:02:24.000Z","msg":"中央集權 + 君主制"},{"pid":"d2c6fd3fcb93a120f205740cdbeeffc0dbce8613","tid":1013220,"uid":46245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"如果真係67歲算係咁啦，不過他信個妹英祿好j好多"},{"pid":"feac338c87f770ef52a6d57b26aec1b0728c0f89","tid":1013220,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"嚴格來講，<br />\n泰國